# OpenCoreAnalysisKit Java Heap 遍历与类实例 Check 机制深度分析

## 1. 整体架构

该项目通过 `space --check` 命令实现对 coredump 中 Java heap 的完整遍历和对象检查：

```
cmd_space.cpp (命令入口)
    ↓
Android::ForeachObjects() (遍历所有 space)
    ↓
Space::Walk() (每个空间独立遍历)
    ↓
ContinuousSpaceBitmap::VisitMarkedRange() / 线性扫描
    ↓
JavaVerify::verify() (对象类型检查)
    ↓
VerifyClassObject / VerifyArrayObject / VerifyInstanceObject (具体检查)
```

## 2. 核心遍历流程

### 2.1 入口：Android::ForeachObjects

**源码位置**：`android/android.cpp:384-428`

```cpp
void Android::ForeachObjects(std::function<bool (art::mirror::Object& object)> fn, int flag, bool check) {
    art::Runtime& runtime = art::Runtime::Current();
    art::gc::Heap& heap = runtime.GetHeap();

    auto walkfn = [&](art::gc::space::Space* space) {
        if (space->IsVaildSpace()) {
            space->Walk(fn, check);  // 关键：调用每个 space 的 Walk
        }
    };

    // 遍历连续空间
    for (const auto& space : heap.GetContinuousSpaces()) {
        if (space->IsImageSpace()) { ... }
        else if (space->IsZygoteSpace()) { ... }
        else if (space->IsRegionSpace() || space->IsBumpPointerSpace()) { ... }
        else if (space->IsMallocSpace()) { ... }
        else if (space->IsFakeSpace()) { ... }
    }

    // 遍历不连续空间
    for (const auto& space : heap.GetDiscontinuousSpaces()) {
        walkfn(space.get());
    }
}
```

**遍历标志**：
- `EACH_APP_OBJECTS` — App 进程空间 (RegionSpace/BumpPointerSpace)
- `EACH_ZYGOTE_OBJECTS` — Zygote 空间
- `EACH_IMAGE_OBJECTS` — Boot Image 空间
- `EACH_FAKE_OBJECTS` — 伪空间

### 2.2 RegionSpace 遍历（主要 heap 空间）

**源码位置**：`android/art/runtime/gc/space/region_space.cpp:209-267`

```cpp
void RegionSpace::Walk(std::function<bool (mirror::Object& object)> fn, bool check) {
    WalkInternal(fn, false, check);
}

void RegionSpace::WalkInternal(...) {
    Region regions_(regions(), this);
    uint64_t num_regions_ = num_regions();

    for (int i = 0; i < num_regions_; ++i) {
        Region r(regions_.Ptr() + i * SIZEOF(Region), regions_);

        if (r.IsLarge()) {
            // 大对象直接遍历
            mirror::Object object = r.Begin();
            if (object.GetClass().Ptr() != 0x0)
                visitor(object);
        } else {
            // 非大对象区域使用 bitmap 或线性扫描
            WalkNonLargeRegion(visitor, r, check);
        }
    }
}

void RegionSpace::WalkNonLargeRegion(...) {
    const bool need_bitmap = region.LiveBytes() != (top - pos);

    if (need_bitmap) {
        // 使用 GC mark bitmap 精确定位存活对象
        GetLiveBitmap().VisitMarkedRange(pos, top, visitor, check);
    } else {
        // 线性扫描：从 begin 到 top，步进 kObjectAlignment (8 bytes)
        while (pos < top) {
            mirror::Object object(pos, object_cache);
            if (object.IsNonLargeValid()) {
                visitor(object);
                pos = GetNextObject(object);
            } else {
                pos = object.NextValidOffset(top);
                if (check) LOGE("Region:[...] has bad object!!");
            }
        }
    }
}
```

### 2.3 Bitmap 精确定位算法

**源码位置**：`android/art/runtime/gc/accounting/space_bitmap.cpp:69-166`

```cpp
void ContinuousSpaceBitmap::VisitMarkedRange(uint64_t visit_begin, uint64_t visit_end,
                                             std::function<bool (mirror::Object& object)> visitor, bool check) {
    // 将地址范围转换为 bitmap index
    uint64_t offset_start = visit_begin - heap_begin_ref.Ptr();
    uint64_t index_start = OffsetToIndex(offset_start, point_bit);

    // 遍历逻辑：
    // Index(begin)  ...    Index(end)
    // [xxxxx???][........][????yyyy]

    // 1. 处理左边界（不完整的 word）
    uint64_t left_edge = bitmap_begin_ref.valueOf((index_start * point_bit));
    left_edge &= ~((1 << bit_start) - 1);

    // 2. 遍历中间的完整 words
    for (uint64_t i = index_start + 1; i < index_end; ++i) {
        uint64_t w = bitmap_begin_ref.valueOf((i * point_bit));
        if (w != 0) {
            do {
                uint64_t shift = __builtin_ctzll(w);  // 找最低 set bit
                mirror::Object obj(ptr_base + shift * kObjectAlignment);
                if (obj.IsNonLargeValid())
                    visitor(obj);
                w ^= (1 << shift);  // 清除已处理的 bit
            } while (w != 0);
        }
    }

    // 3. 处理右边界
    right_edge &= ((1 << bit_end) - 1);
    ...
}
```

**Bitmap 原理**：
- 每个 bit 对应 `kObjectAlignment * point_size` 字节的 heap 区域
- 默认 `point_size=8`，即每个 bit 标记 64 字节
- 使用 `__builtin_ctzll` 找最低 set bit，实现 O(n_存活对象) 复杂度

## 3. 对象有效性检查

### 3.1 Object::IsNonLargeValid

**源码位置**：`android/art/runtime/mirror/object.cpp:176-198`

```cpp
bool Object::IsNonLargeValid() {
    try {
        Class klass_ = GetClass();
        // 1. klass 不能为 0 或 kPoisonDeadObject
        if (klass_.Ptr() == 0x0 || klass_.Ptr() == kPoisonDeadObject)
            return false;

        // 2. klass 必须是 Class 类实例
        if (LIKELY(klass_.IsClass())) {
            int64_t thiz_size = SizeOf();
            // 3. 对象大小必须在 [kObjectAlignment, kValidObjectSize) 范围内
            if (LIKELY(!(thiz_size < (int64_t)kObjectAlignment))
                    && LIKELY(thiz_size < kValidObjectSize /* 1MB */)) {
                return true;
            }
        }
    } catch (InvalidAddressException& e) { }
    return false;
}
```

### 3.2 Object 布局

```
+------------------------+
| klass_ (4 bytes)       |  ← 对象头：指向 Class 对象
+------------------------+
| monitor_ (4 bytes)     |  ← 锁信息
+------------------------+
| <instance fields>      |  ← 实例字段
+------------------------+
```

**Object 大小限制**：
- 最小：`kObjectAlignment = 8` bytes
- 最大：`kValidObjectSize = 1MB`（检测超大伪对象）

## 4. 类实例 Check 机制

### 4.1 JavaVerify 验证框架

**源码位置**：`parser/command/android/verify.h:26-48`

```cpp
class JavaVerify {
    constexpr static int CHECK_FULL_BAD_OBJECT = 1 << 0;      // 坏对象检查
    constexpr static int CHECK_FULL_CONFLICT_METHOD = 1 << 1; // 冲突方法检查
    constexpr static int CHECK_FULL_REUSE_DEX_PC_PTR = 1 << 2; // PC 复用检查
    constexpr static int CHECK_FULL_U_EXTENDS_RECORD = 1 << 3; // Record 类检查
    ...
};
```

### 4.2 三类对象检查

**1. Class 对象检查** (`VerifyClassObject`)
```cpp
void JavaVerify::VerifyClassObject(art::mirror::Class& clazz) {
    // 1. 获取所有静态字段
    auto callback = [&](art::ArtField& field) -> bool {
        fields.push_back(field);
        return false;
    };
    Android::ForeachStaticField(current, callback);

    // 2. 获取元类的实例字段
    current = clazz.GetClass();
    Android::ForeachInstanceField(current, callback);

    // 3. 遍历每个字段，检查引用是否有效
    for (auto& field : fields) {
        art::mirror::Object tmp(field.GetObj(clazz), clazz);
        if (tmp.Ptr() && !tmp.IsValid()) {
            LOGE("Class [%p] has bad static field: %s", clazz.Ptr(), field.GetName());
            PrintCommand::PrintField(...);
        }
    }
}
```

**2. Array 对象检查** (`VerifyArrayObject`)
```cpp
void JavaVerify::VerifyArrayObject(art::mirror::Array& array) {
    if (array.IsObjectArray()) {
        for (int32_t i = 0; i < length; ++i) {
            api::MemoryRef ref(array.GetRawData(sizeof(uint32_t), i));
            art::mirror::Object object(*reinterpret_cast<uint32_t*>(ref.Real()));
            if (object.Ptr() && !object.IsValid()) {
                LOGE("Array [%p] element [%d] is bad: 0x%" PRIx64, 
                     array.Ptr(), i, object.Ptr());
            }
        }
    }
}
```

**3. Instance 对象检查** (`VerifyInstanceObject`)
```cpp
void JavaVerify::VerifyInstanceObject(art::mirror::Object& object) {
    art::mirror::Class super = clazz;
    // 遍历类继承链
    do {
        std::vector<art::ArtField> fields;
        Android::ForeachInstanceField(super, callback);

        for (auto& field : fields) {
            if (field.GetTypeDescriptor() == "L...") {  // 只检查对象引用字段
                art::mirror::Object tmp(field.GetObj(object));
                if (tmp.Ptr() && !tmp.IsValid()) {
                    LOGE("Instance [%p] field %s is bad", object.Ptr(), field.GetName());
                }
            }
        }
        super = super.GetSuperClass();  // 向上遍历父类
    } while (super.Ptr());
}
```

## 5. LargeObjectSpace 遍历

**源码位置**：`android/art/runtime/gc/space/large_object_space.cpp:334-348`

```cpp
void LargeObjectMapSpace::Walk(std::function<bool (mirror::Object& object)> visitor, bool check) {
    cxx::map& large_objects_ = GetLargeObjectsCache();
    for (const auto& value : large_objects_) {
        LargeObjectsPair pair = value;
        api::MemoryRef ref = pair.first();  // 获取大对象地址
        if (ref.IsValid()) {
            mirror::Object object(ref);
            if (object.IsValid()) {
                visitor(object);
            } else if (check) {
                LOGE("0x%" PRIx64 " is bad object on %s!!", object.Ptr(), GetName());
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## 6. 核心数据结构总结

| 数据结构 | 用途 | 关键方法 |
|---------|------|---------|
| `gc::Heap` | Heap 入口，获取所有 spaces | `GetContinuousSpaces()`, `GetDiscontinuousSpaces()` |
| `ContinuousSpace` | 连续内存空间基类 | `Walk(fn, check)`, `GetNextObject()` |
| `RegionSpace` | App heap 主空间 | `WalkInternal()`, `WalkNonLargeRegion()` |
| `ContinuousSpaceBitmap` | GC mark bitmap | `VisitMarkedRange()` — bitmap 遍历 |
| `mirror::Object` | Java 对象包装 | `IsValid()`, `IsNonLargeValid()`, `GetClass()` |
| `mirror::Class` | Class 对象 | `GetObjectSize()`, `GetSuperClass()` |
| `JavaVerify` | 对象检查器 | `verify()`, `VerifyClassObject()`, etc. |

## 7. 与 ART 源码的对应关系

| OpenCoreAnalysisKit | 对应 AOSP ART |
|---------------------|---------------|
| `RegionSpace::Walk` | `art::gc::space::RegionSpace::Walk` |
| `ContinuousSpaceBitmap::VisitMarkedRange` | `art::gc::accounting::ContinuousSpaceBitmap::VisitMarkedRange` |
| `Object::IsNonLargeValid` | ART 没有完全相同的函数，但逻辑对应 heap verification |
| `JavaVerify` | 对应 `VerifyHeapReferences` (heap.h) |

---

